Class IterableStringTokenizer

java.lang.Object
java.util.StringTokenizer
org.apache.commons.lang3.util.IterableStringTokenizer
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<String>, Enumeration<Object>
public class IterableStringTokenizer extends StringTokenizer implements Iterable<String>
A StringTokenizer that implements Iterable<String> and conversion methods toList() and toStream().
Since:
3.18.0
